songs.title: 1975(TheBedRoomGroove)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]

What's goin' on
You don't gotta tell me nothing
You don't gotta tell me nothing

[Verse]

You don't gotta tell me nothing
You don't gotta say a word
You don't gotta run in hind, it's your world
You don't gotta tell me lies
You don't gotta act your age
You can outlaw all you want, I'll wait
